{"id":"hq-004","title":"Add backoff timing to witness patrol formula","description":"dispatched_by: mayor\n\nThe witness patrol formula cycles too fast, sending 10+ pings to deacon in 30 seconds.\n\nRoot cause: mol-witness-patrol.formula.toml loop-or-exit step creates a new wisp and continues immediately without any delay.\n\nFix: Add await-signal with backoff (similar to deacon patrol) in the loop-or-exit step. Suggested: 30s base, 5m max backoff.\n\nAffected file: .beads/formulas/mol-witness-patrol.formula.toml","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"bug","assignee":"gastown_boy/polecats/nux","owner":"will@saults.io","created_at":"2026-01-12T14:41:06.928541-06:00","created_by":"mayor","updated_at":"2026-01-12T14:47:45.132873-06:00","closed_at":"2026-01-12T14:47:45.132873-06:00","close_reason":"Added await-signal with backoff (30s base, 2x multiplier, 5m max) to loop-or-exit step in mol-witness-patrol.formula.toml"}
